snippet.title: "klocki"
snippet.description:
"klocki" is my second puzzle game after successful "Hook".
Its a relaxing game, that is loaded with a lot of different features.

Your goal is to connect different types of lines together. Calming music and sounds were made by Wojciech Wasiak. 

Thanks for playing and your support!

More at: http://klockigame.com
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/klocki/id1105390093
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.klockigame.klocki
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/499440/


https://twitter.com/targaciej
